<h2 id="why-it-is-problematic-to-nest-information">Why it is problematic to nest information</h2>

<p>If content is nested by using tabs, accordions or tool tips, the page appears more organized and structured. However, the complexity of the page and how to use it increases.</p>

<h4 class="no_toc mb-5" id="the-following-problems-may-occur">The following problems may occur:</h4>

<ul>
  <li>Users overlook content</li>
  <li>If unsuitable contents are nested, the usability for all users is reduced</li>
  <li>The demands on cross-device design are increasing</li>
  <li>For all users and users with disabilities, the site becomes more complicated to use with screen reader and keyboard</li>
</ul>

